风波？<br/>3.遗传学与自然选择学说之间有什么关系？为何自然选择学说一度被冷落，然后又获得关注？<br/>4.《物种起源》的思想有哪些来源？<br/>5.达尔文的朋友华莱士对《物种起源》有什么贡献？<br/>6.进化论和宇宙大爆炸理论有什么关系吗？</p></section></section></section></section><img style="margin-top: -0.8em; width: 100%; float: left; text-align: start;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appWawLB9IH1520/image/ueditor/14817000_1558604073.png"/> <section style="clear: both;"></section></section></section><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; position: static;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;"><section style="padding-right: 12px; padding-left: 12px; color: rgb(199, 182, 140);"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">购买须知</p></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; margin-top: -14px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 100%; float: right; margin-top: -14px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></section><section style="clear: both;"></section></section><section style="border: 1px solid rgb(218, 203, 158); margin-top: -12px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 0px;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin: 5px 0%; position: static;"><section style="text-align: left; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><em>1. 《物种起源》专栏共3段音频，共55分钟。</em></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><em style="letter-spacing: 0px;">2. 《物种起源》为付费音频专栏，成功购买即可永久性收听本产品的内容（非可抗力等其他因素除外）；</em></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><em>3.本书单为在线虚拟产品，一经购买，概不退款。</em></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; position: static;"><section style="width: 100%; padding: 1em 10px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-125252